{"tid":1147966,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] PES Mobile 2019 討論貼 (105)  英超盛世","createTime":"2019-05-10T07:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T06:15:21.000Z","uid":152516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"213567c628fea380d0ced5aaf5ee0dc8a815c02a","tid":1147966,"uid":152516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T07:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZdwQZXy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdwQZXy.png&h=2e1408c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n● 官網：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.konami.com%2Fwepes%2Fmobile%2Fen%2F&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGtE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=e7e4048c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/</a><br />\n● Download Link<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fpes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer%2Fid1117270703%3Fmt%3D8&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGtE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=3dc0d182\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.konami.pesam&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGtE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=7fe2c4cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam</a><br />\n<br />\n● 新手開波Q&amp;A?<br />\n<br />\n1. 洗唔洗刷首抽?<br />\n新手開波既時候會有好多抽，盡量雙金/一黑起手，抽中既球員可以睇下下面既推薦List，如果無亦可以問下各位巴打，當然唔滿意既可以繼續刷到自己想要既球員為止。<br />\n<br />\n2. 點樣儲錢?<br />\n一開始既時候你會好窮，所以盡量用白銅銀波儲GP，例如用白銅銀波打活動或者用123星球探抽球員放，但隊中有一兩隻金黑都負擔得起。<br />\n<br />\n打季節賽-手動/sim : 升班23000gp 留班12000gp <br />\n記得用3個唔同教練打sim/手動/巡迴賽活動，方便教練續約<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣改Email或者密碼?<br />\n<a href=\"https://my.konami.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.konami.net%2F&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGtE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=f4402d7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://my.konami.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 操控方法<br />\n操控類型有 Advanced 同 Classic 揀<br />\n推薦 Classic 佢類似手制咁樣同埋易上手啲<br />\n<br />\n● 球員資料<br />\nPES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2019%2F&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGtE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=1e7f39e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2019/</a><br />\n要注意由於可能有球員更新，所以DATABASE 入面既100%抽球員可能有誤。<br />\n<br />\n只需要直接search球員名，你就可以搵到該球員特性同數值。<br />\n而想搵一堆某類球員，可以憑Search Conditions自行set Filters 搵出黎。<br />\n<br />\n●畫面調整<br />\n新手入game 第一件事畫質轉60fps<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h38hp4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh38hp4m.jpg&h=66c1328d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但30fps low quality 比較慳電<br />\n<br />\n教練，球員，沒有最強只有更強<br />\n因該每次更新，Konami 都會暗改教練球員走位，唔會通知，要靠老手用過先知<br />\n<br />\n●實時系統<br />\n每周四維護6小時（10am-4pm)後，會按照現實球員表現而調整球員狀態；<br />\n另有巴打（牛佬）隨時更新球員實際操作表現（暗改），詳情要留意留言<br />\n<br />\n●教練更新<br />\n即日起，可簽入不同版本的同名教練。每日更新3次，已擁有的教練不能再簽下<br />\n<br />\n●抽球員種類<br />\n1box draw<br />\n普通版<br />\n傳奇球員<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nF07oNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnF07oNa.jpg&h=30156fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2限時精選球員FP(目前只限2019)<br />\n基本分三種，每種限3抽<br />\nPlayer of the week<br />\nClub selection<br />\nJ.League<br />\n<br />\n3普通pool<br />\n按位置分，另有日職pool<br />\n<br />\n●交易球員<br />\n擁有三名相同（同名同色）的球員，現在你可以用他們來獲取一名相同稀有度（同色）的新球員｡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJ3Qmw2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJ3Qmw2.png&h=5caf8d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n●拍賣<br />\n根本球員條件（國籍，球會，年歲，能力）買球探組合球員<br />\n詳情：PES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2019%2F&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGtE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=1e7f39e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2019/</a><br />\n<br />\n●新物品登場<br />\n1協助球員學習新技巧：只能添加一招<br />\n2提升球員的位置適合度：ratings會較高<br />\n3教練的管理技巧：更高cost"},{"pid":"f5177a16b45eeb6f41c35a5ecd5163b1f17dfef9","tid":1147966,"uid":152516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"@emily<br />\n真心封ac咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a84583e890b66499aeec45d532ae18069a5881","tid":1147966,"uid":32387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:15:21.000Z","msg":"Any pvp?"}]}